      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To direct the Director of the National Science Foundation to establish a Chief Diversity Officer position and to develop a strategic plan to ensure participation in NSF activities by a diverse group of learners, researchers, and institutions.</title>
